# Design Tokens

All values must come from CSS custom properties defined in `src/app/globals.css` and mirrored in `design-system/css/variables.css`. Never use raw hex values or pixel literals for colors, fonts, or spacing.

## Color-to-Token Mapping

| Purpose                  | Token                          | Value     |
|--------------------------|--------------------------------|-----------|
| Page background (dark)   | `var(--bg-dark)` / `var(--color-night)` | `#090909` |
| Light section bg         | `var(--color-light)`           | `#F7F8FB` |
| Smoke / divider bg       | `var(--color-smoke)`           | `#D9D9D9` |
| Pure white               | `var(--color-white)` / `var(--white)` | `#FFFFFF` |
| Pure black               | `var(--color-black)` / `var(--black)` | `#000000` |
| Footer grey text         | `var(--color-grey-400)` / `var(--grey)` | `#A5A9AC` |
| Blog meta grey           | `var(--color-grey-300)`        | `#C3C3C3` |
| Dark border / separator  | `var(--color-grey-700)`        | `#333333` |
| Purple accent            | `var(--color-purple-500)` / `var(--purple)` | `#9662FF` |
| Magenta accent           | `var(--color-purple-900)` / `var(--magenta)` | `#A401B7` |

## Font Families — Never Use Raw Font Names

| Font                  | Token                  | Usage                                         |
|-----------------------|------------------------|-----------------------------------------------|
| Manrope               | `var(--font-primary)`  | All body text, headings, navigation, buttons   |
| Libre Baskerville     | `var(--font-serif)`    | Author names, section tag text, serif accents  |
| Lexend                | `var(--font-accent)`   | Counter numbers (stat counters)                |

## Spacing — Always Use `var(--space-*)` Tokens

Common values: `--space-4` (4px), `--space-8` (8px), `--space-12` (12px), `--space-16` (16px), `--space-20` (20px), `--space-24` (24px), `--space-32` (32px), `--space-40` (40px), `--space-48` (48px), `--space-60` (60px), `--space-80` (80px), `--space-120` (120px).

Section vertical padding: always `var(--section-padding)` (120px).

## Borders

- Dark background separators: `1px solid #333` (use `var(--color-grey-700)`)
- Light background separators: `1px solid #c3c3c3` (use `var(--color-grey-300)`)
- Button / interactive borders: `1px solid var(--white)` on dark, `1px solid var(--black)` on light

## Section Backgrounds — Only These Are Allowed

- `var(--bg-dark)` — `#090909` (primary dark)
- `var(--color-smoke)` — `#D9D9D9` (divider / accent)
- `var(--color-white)` — `#FFFFFF` (light sections)
- `var(--color-light)` — `#F7F8FB` (subtle light)
